<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Elisabeth von Bayern, Markgräfin von Brandenburg und Burggräfin von Nürnberg</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass ihm keine flüchtigen Juden zu Nürnberg bekannt sind und er sich wegen eines Versprechens einiger Juden an die Adressatin nicht äußern kann, da er nicht weiß, um wen es sich handelt.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_194" id="96r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_194_r1l11">Frawen Elıſabeth <expan>Marggrefin<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>Brandemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_194_r1l12">vnd <expan>Burggrefin<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> etc <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>g<ex>nedigen</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>aw</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_194_r1l13">Gnedıge fraw / als vns eẅr <expan>durchleẅchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan> hat <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_194_r1l14"><expan>etlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> Juden / bey vns <expan>geſeſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe flüchtıg <expan>ſull<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> ſein . weıb kınder </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_194_r1l15">vnd hab ʒu <expan>beküm<ex>m</ex>ern</expan> etc . das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> Nu <expan>wıſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_194_r1l16">ʒu dıſen <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>kein<ex>en</ex></expan> Juden bey vns <expan>geſeſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / der flüchtıg ſey / Vnd als vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_194_r1l17">eẅr <expan>furſtenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade fürbas <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von vvort <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> . dıe etlıch <expan>Jude<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_194_r1l18">bey vns eẅr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> . <expan>ſull<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſprochen</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . mag eẅr gnade wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteen</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_194_r1l19">daʒ wır darcʒu niht wol <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> können / wan vns niht <expan>wıſſenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> ıſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_194_r1l20">welh <expan>dıeſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> Juden <expan>ſull<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein . Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>durchleẅchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> dıenſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_194_line_1577090200329_1839">vnd <expan>wolgefall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_194" id="96r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Frawen Elisabeth, <expan>marggrefin<ex>n</ex></expan> zu
                                <expan>Brandemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> und
                            <expan>burggrefin<ex>n</ex></expan> zu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
                        etc., <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>g<ex>nedigen</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>aw</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnedige fraw, als uns ewr <expan>durchlewchtik<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan> hat
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>etlich<ex>er</ex></expan> juden bey uns
                            <expan>gesess<ex>en</ex></expan>, die flüchtig
                            <expan>sull<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> sein, weib, kinder und hab zu
                                <expan>beküm<ex>m</ex>ern</expan> etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>.
                        Nu <expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan> wir zu disen
                            <expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>kein<ex>en</ex></expan> juden bey uns
                            <expan>gesess<ex>en</ex></expan>, der flüchtig sey, und als uns ewr
                                <expan>furstenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade fürbas
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von wort
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die etlich
                            <expan>jude<ex>n</ex></expan> bey uns ewr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>sull<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>sprochen</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, mag ewr gnade wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan>, daz wir darczu niht wol
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> können, wan uns niht
                                <expan>wissenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> ist, welh
                                <expan>dies<ex>elben</ex></expan> juden
                            <expan>sull<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>durchlewchtik<ex>eit</ex></expan> dienst und
                                <expan>wolgefall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
